Package: SAMprior
Type: Package
Title: Self-adapting Mixture (SAM) Priors 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Peng Yang, Ying Yuan
Maintainer: Peng Yang <py11@rice.edu>
Description: The SAMprior package is designed to calculate the SAM prior and
    generate its operating characteristics for dynamically borrowing information
    from historical data.
